{"tid":1727524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實出解放軍係國際核彈嘅另一論調","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:45:01.000Z","uid":181474,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d7fa0a6c2e2c94bc88279910138c600246ac02a0","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"今日記者們放問到嘅解放軍啊頭就聲稱<br />\n佢哋係&ldquo;自發出嚟清潔&rdquo;<br />\n可以點樣理解<span style=\"color: red;\">自發</span>呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自發姐係軍人運用自由意志，唔理會指令而行動</span></span><br />\n亦即係代表文官無法控制武官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺國際嚟講，呢種行為可以導致<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事政變</span></span><br />\n依家我哋只需要煲大<span style=\"color: red;\">自發</span>呢個term<br />\n即係依家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">駐港解放軍</span></span>可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無視文官</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">駐軍法</span></span><br />\n即將進入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真。軍政府</span></span>時代<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極需要其他國家出兵保護在港僑民利益</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b5e25c1d09a8e72780af0de3607825887b1091","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a353c5bb4ccb49477cfc4dca800ac2e36c9aa366","tid":1727524,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/76720846_2681514415245123_6957976255085936640_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQlICmWQoqDDmLbSngql6JkutH1TMH36i4Vq6LH4ha4APQTgAndd2BlnoB9nSV40V94&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;oh=f0181f546e40a18b64046c785825002c&amp;oe=5E48E30D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F76720846_2681514415245123_6957976255085936640_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQlICmWQoqDDmLbSngql6JkutH1TMH36i4Vq6LH4ha4APQTgAndd2BlnoB9nSV40V94%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26oh%3Df0181f546e40a18b64046c785825002c%26oe%3D5E48E30D&h=6c309869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afcaf26168094456445cdbc6f8bb0438aef85b5d","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bbd74f57ef50a79bcf344a6d2457ff00ae3eb3","tid":1727524,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=33c22514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=7dd6f081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"54a62b0396fcad7aa1160671216ca65458cf8021","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e468b5fd8ad02ee396034d8f5f666c5802e7b76c","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c540e03d6b6f91a73de5176f941c2c9ee42f88","tid":1727524,"uid":264984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"入紙申請禁制令再煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d219ab86fb1ef4b279790b8c66696eadcee52d","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289e7574d903c6e411d673306ef2aeab5519b374","tid":1727524,"uid":184985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n自發殺害香港人都得？"},{"pid":"5d16e678adc4a5b393c8e4cbcddaa2a9126cfb53","tid":1727524,"uid":181474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":